Agent Raghav -- Crime Branch is an Indian crime fiction anthology television series , which premiered on & TV from 5 September 2015 to 10 April 2016 for one hour at Saturday and Sunday nights .
The series was produced by Contiloe Entertainment of Abhimanyu Singh and starred Sharad Kelkar in the eponymous role of Agent Raghav Sinha , along with Aahana Kumra , Deepali Pansare , Danish Pandor , Jason Tham and Mahesh Manjrekar , the latter appeared in a recurring role .
The serial received Indian Telly Awards in the category of Best Thriller and Horror Show and was also nominated for Best Weekend Show .
The show is said to be inspired from the American police drama/mystery television series , '' The Mentalist .